I authorize YMCA OF METROPOLITAN LOS ANGELES, and the financial institution designated to begin deductions as per my instruction for regular recurring payment(s) and/or one-time payment(s). This authority is to remain in effect until YMCA OF METROPOLITAN LOS ANGELES has received notification from me of its change or termination. This notification must be received at least ten (10) business days before the next debit is scheduled at the address provided below.

YMCA OF METROPOLITAN LOS ANGELES
937 Enterprise Dr
Sacramento CA 95825
(111) 111-1111

YMCA OF METROPOLITAN LOS ANGELES may not assign this authorization, whether directly or indirectly, by operation of law, change of control or otherwise, without providing at least 10 days prior written notice to me. I have certain recourse rights if any debit does not comply with this agreement.
